      <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Making child arrangements if you divorce or separate</h1>

      <p class="govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Contents</p>
      <ul class="govuk-list govuk-body-s govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
        <li>— <a href="https://www.gov.uk/looking-after-children-divorce" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-underline">Overview</a>
        </li>
        <li>— Make a child arrangements plan</li>
        <li>— <a href="https://www.gov.uk/looking-after-children-divorce/mediation" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-underline">Make an agreement through mediation</a>
        </li>
        <li>— <a href="https://www.gov.uk/looking-after-children-divorce/non-court-dispute-resolution" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-underline">Other ways to agree without going to court</a>
        </li>
        <li>— <a href="https://www.gov.uk/looking-after-children-divorce/apply-for-court-order" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-underline">Apply for a court order</a>
        </li>
        <li>— <a href="https://www.gov.uk/looking-after-children-divorce/after-you-apply-for-a-court-order">After you apply for a court order</a>
        </li>
        <li>— <a href="https://www.gov.uk/looking-after-children-divorce/change-or-enforce-an-order" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-underline">Change or enforce an order</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
