      <div class="app-heading govuk-!-margin-bottom-6">
        <h1 class="app-heading__text govuk-heading-xl">
          Make a child arrangements plan
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div data-module="govspeak" class="app-govspeak govuk-govspeak app-govspeak--direction-ltr js-disable-youtube govuk-!-margin-bottom-0" data-govspeak-module-started="true">

        <p>You do not have to do any official paperwork if you agree about child arrangements.</p>

        <p>You can write down what you’ve agreed in a ‘child arrangements plan’ if you want a record.</p>

        <p>You can use this service to help you plan and agree on child arrangements. It creates a document which you can share with the other parent to ask for their agreement and suggestions.</p>

        <p>You can also use the service with the other parent to make a plan together.</p>

        <h2 id="what-the-plan-includes">What the plan includes</h2>
        <p>You’ll be asked to suggest details about how you plan to look after your children, such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>when and where they spend time with each parent</li>
          <li>when and what other types of contact take place (phone calls, for example)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="when-to-use-this-service">When to use this service</h2>
        <p>You can use this service if you either:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>have no child arrangements in place yet</li>
          <li>want to suggest changes to your existing arrangements</li>
        </ul>

        <div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
          <p>You should not use this service if you already have a court order that sets out child arrangements you and your ex-partner must follow. You can <a href="https://www.gov.uk/looking-after-children-divorce/change-or-enforce-an-order">change or enforce an order</a> instead.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 id="make-your-plan">Make your plan</h2>
        <p>Any plan you create using this service is not legally binding. The other parent does not have to do what it says and either of you can suggest changes to it at any time.</p>
        <div role="note" aria-label="Information" class="application-notice info-notice">
          <p>Do not use this service if you feel pressured or intimidated into using it. If you or your children are at immediate risk of harm, call 999 and ask for the police. Find out how to <a href="https://www.gov.uk/guidance/domestic-abuse-how-to-get-help">get help if you’re a victim of domestic abuse</a>.</p>
        </div>

        {% if includeWelshLanguage %}
          {% if getLocale() == 'cy' %}
            {{ govukInsetText({
              html: 'Ma\'er gwasanaeth hwn hefyd ar gael yn <a href="?lang=en" class="govuk-link govuk-link--no-underline">Saesneg (English)</a>'
            }) }}
